{"tid":1884954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《沙燕》雜誌創刊","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T03:50:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be88f4bc41c5d60e2d2fae9bce56a8ad7b171e04","tid":1884954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"沙田新幹綫<br />\n&middot; 16 February &middot; <br />\n <br />\n嘩！！！原來有班有心人整咗屬於沙田人嘅雜誌，大家快啲follow佢地telegram了解多啲啦！佢地仲話歡迎大家投稿呀！<br />\n<br />\n佢地既telegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/shatinmartin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshatinmartin&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=b7636659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/shatinmartin</a><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n《沙燕》&mdash;&mdash;屬於沙田人嘅一本雜誌<br />\n<br />\n本刊受《荃真機》啓發，因而創刊。冀可以聯繫沙田人，突破溫層。人人皆可投稿，讓大眾心聲多一個渠道可以發表。<br />\n<br />\n投稿/意見/課金：<a href=\"http://t.me/shatin_martin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshatin_martin&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=41ccbe8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/shatin_martin</a><br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Snapian/photos/a.791277410908226/2797919226910691/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSnapian%2Fphotos%2Fa.791277410908226%2F2797919226910691%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=245765ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Snapian/photos/a.791277410908226/2797919226910691/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"add3829f01d1eea4897053c02958e074901cee9b","tid":1884954,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fmel5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/85084418_2797919233577357_1427277796362682368_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ohc=8ATVfm4kX7EAX9E6h_L&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fmel5-1.fna&amp;oh=02039507b87798e9e8ae9e9e640b0af7&amp